{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/new-002/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"1999 TCG 同人卡片游戏 V0.1.0-SNACSHORTS"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f0d9b907-4acf-5399-bc27-08cd622ccc74","excerpt":"…","html":"<p>如你所见，我们开发了这个演练场的雏形。其目的是为了以后测试卡和规则。\n打印的速度太慢了，我也需要一个方法完成自己和自己战斗的这件事。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/news/%E6%BC%94%E7%BB%83%E5%9C%BA.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"/playground\">如果你感兴趣可以点击这里</a></p>\n<p>当然还有很多问题。比如：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>不能动态设置卡组</li>\n<li>没有卡组和目的的检索</li>\n<li>没有士气值（血条）</li>\n<li>没有时代值</li>\n<li>或许应该加个流程或者日志什么的</li>\n</ul>\n<p>总之这是一个雏形。我希望越来越好。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>实现拖拽效果基于<code class=\"language-text\">react-dnd</code></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"发布了测试版的演练场","date":"September 01, 2024","description":"发布了测试版的演练场"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/S001-A-006/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"玛蒂尔达"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/S001-T-004/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"晒晒眼睛"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"f0d9b907-4acf-5399-bc27-08cd622ccc74","previousPostId":"7b9bd9d1-3c37-5c26-ae80-dccf72f3cb4a","nextPostId":"a9e69745-0d02-5c91-8fc4-bb8ef1d55991"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"],"slicesMap":{}}